<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>CCATT Viewer Rounding Survey</title>
  	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../jQuery/jquery.mobile-1.1.1.min.css">
	<script src="../jQuery/jquery-1.7.1.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../jQuery/jquery.mobile-1.1.1.min.js"></script></head>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="./stylesheets/main.css">
	/*<style>*/
	/*	#form2 { */
	/*	    background:rgb(253, 234, 255);*/
	/*	}*/
	/*</style>*/
</head>
<body>
<!--<div data-role="page" data-url="/survey2" style="background:rgb(253, 234, 255);">-->
<div data-role="page" data-url="/survey2" id="form2">
    <form action="/survey2" method="POST">
        <h2>CCATT Viewer Rounding Survey</h2>
		<p><strong>After accessing the viewer</strong></p>
		<p>Directions: For the following questions please select your responses</p>
	
		<ol>
		  <li>
		    Having reviewed the last 24 hrs during rounds and seen the 24hr CCATT Viewer screen, I feel that in the past 24hrs this patient has shown evidence of:
		    <div class="ui-grid-a">
		      <div class="ui-block-a">
		      	<ol type='a' start='1'>
		          <li>
		            Infection
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
			          <label for="qa1-1-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA1_1" id="qa1-1-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa1-1-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA1_1" id="qa1-1-2" value="no">
			          <label for="qa1-1-3">Unsure</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA1_1" id="qa1-1-3" value="unsure">
			        </fieldset>
		          </li>
		          <li>
		            Hemodynamic instability
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
			          <label for="qa1-2-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA1_2" id="qa1-2-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa1-2-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA1_2" id="qa1-2-2" value="no">	 
			          <label for="qa1-2-3">Unsure</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA1_2" id="qa1-2-3" value="unsure">
			        </fieldset>
		          </li>
		        </ol>
		      </div>
		      <div class="ui-block-b">
		      	<ol type='a' start='3'>
		          <li>
		            Uncontrolled bleeding
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
		              <label for="qa1-3-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA1_3" id="qa1-3-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa1-3-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA1_3" id="qa1-3-2" value="no">	 
			          <label for="qa1-3-3">Unsure</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA1_3" id="qa1-3-3" value="unsure">
		            </fieldset>
		          </li>
		          <li>
		            Respiratory deterioration
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
			          <label for="qa1-4-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA1_4" id="qa1-4-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa1-4-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA1_4" id="qa1-4-2" value="no">	 
			          <label for="qa1-4-3">Unsure</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA1_4" id="qa1-4-3" value="unsure">
		            </fieldset>
		          </li>
		      	</ol>
		    </div>
		  </li>
		  <li>
		    Over the past 24hrs the patient’s condition has…
		    <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
			    <label for="qa2-1">Improved significantly</label>
		        <input type="radio" name="QA2" id="qa2-1" value="1" required>
			    <label for="qa2-2">Improved Slightly</label>
			    <input type="radio" name="QA2" id="qa2-2" value="2">
			    <label for="qa2-3">Unchanged</label>
			    <input type="radio" name="QA2" id="qa2-3" value="3">
			    <label for="qa2-4">Deteriorated slightly</label>
			    <input type="radio" name="QA2" id="qa2-4" value="4">
			    <label for="qa2-5">Deteriorated significantly</label>
			    <input type="radio" name="QA2" id="qa2-5" value="5">
			</fieldset>
		  </li>
		</ol>
		<div class="ui-grid-a">
		  <div class="ui-block-a">
		  	<ol start="3">
			    <li>
			      Can the patient be transferred to a lower level of care?
			      <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
				    <label for="qa3-1">Yes</label>
			        <input type="radio" name="QA3" id="qa3-1" value="yes" required>
				    <label for="qa3-2">No</label>
				    <input type="radio" name="QA3" id="qa3-2" value="no">
			      </fieldset>
			    </li>
		    </ol>
		  </div>
		  <div class="ui-block-b">
		  	<ol start="4">
			    <li>
			      Does the patient need to be transferred to a higher level of care?
			      <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
				    <label for="qa4-1">Yes</label>
			        <input type="radio" name="QA4" id="qa4-1" value="yes" required>
				    <label for="qa4-2">No</label>
				    <input type="radio" name="QA4" id="qa4-2" value="no">
				    <label for="qa4-3">N/A</label>
				    <input type="radio" name="QA4" id="qa4-3" value="na">
				  </fieldset>
			    </li>
		    </ol>
		  </div>
		</div>
		<div class="ui-grid-a">
		  <div class="ui-block-a">
		  	<ol start="5">
			    <li>
			      Does this patient have a traumatic brain injury?
			      <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
				    <label for="qa5-1">Yes</label>
			        <input type="radio" name="QA5" id="qa5-1" value="yes" required>
				    <label for="qa5-2">No</label>
				    <input type="radio" name="QA5" id="qa5-2" value="no">
				  </fieldset>
			    </li>
		    </ol>
		  </div>
		  <div class="ui-block-b">
		  	<ol start="6">
			    <li>
			      Is the patient having any ICP problems within the last 24hrs?
			      <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
				    <label for="qa6-1">Yes</label>
			        <input type="radio" name="QA6" id="qa6-1" value="yes" required>
				    <label for="qa6-2">No</label>
				    <input type="radio" name="QA6" id="qa6-2" value="no">
				    <label for="qa6-3">Unsure</label>
				    <input type="radio" name="QA6" id="qa6-3" value="unsure">
				    <label for="qa6-4">N/A</label>
				    <input type="radio" name="QA6" id="qa6-4" value="na">
				  </fieldset>
			    </li>
		    </ol>
		  </div>
		</div>
		<ol start="7">  
		  <li>
		    Due to seeing the viewer, are you planning on any of the following interventions?
		    <div class="ui-grid-a">
		      <div class="ui-block-a">
		        <ol type='a' start='1'>
		          <li>
		            Changing any current medications?
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
			          <label for="qa7-1-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA7_1" id="qa7-1-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa7-1-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA7_1" id="qa7-1-2" value="no">
			        </fieldset>
			      </li>
		          <li>
		            Ordering additional medications?
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
			          <label for="qa7-2-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA7_2" id="qa7-2-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa7-2-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA7_2" id="qa7-2-2" value="no">	 
			        </fieldset>
		          </li>		  
		          <li>
		            Ordering additional diagnostic tests?
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
			          <label for="qa7-3-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA7_3" id="qa7-3-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa7-3-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA7_3" id="qa7-3-2" value="no">	 
			        </fieldset>
		          </li>
		          <li>
		            Changing ventilation settings?
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
			          <label for="qa7-4-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA7_4" id="qa7-4-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa7-4-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA7_4" id="qa7-4-2" value="no">	 
			        </fieldset>
		          </li>
		        </ol>
		      </div>
		      <div class="ui-block-b">
		        <ol type='a' start='5'>
		          <li>
		            Ordering additional labs?
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
			          <label for="qa7-5-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA7_5" id="qa7-5-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa7-5-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA7_5" id="qa7-5-2" value="no">
			        </fieldset>
			      </li>
		          <li>
		            Physically re-examining this patient?
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
				      <label for="qa7-6-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA7_6" id="qa7-6-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa7-6-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA7_6" id="qa7-6-2" value="no">
			        </fieldset>
			      </li>
		          <li>
		            Providing a Fluid Bolus?
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
				      <label for="qa7-7-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA7_7" id="qa7-7-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa7-7-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA7_7" id="qa7-7-2" value="no">
			        </fieldset>
			      </li>
		          <li>
		            Providing a Blood Transfusion?
		            <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
			          <label for="qa7-8-1">Yes</label>
		              <input type="radio" name="QA7_8" id="qa7-8-1" value="yes" required>
			          <label for="qa7-8-2">No</label>
			          <input type="radio" name="QA7_8" id="qa7-8-2" value="no">
			        </fieldset>
			      </li>
			    </ol>
			  </div>
			</div>
		  </li>
		  <li>
		    I found that the CCATT viewer enhanced my understanding of the patient’s condition.
		    <fieldset data-role="controlgroup" data-type="horizontal" data-role="fieldcontain">
			    <label for="qa8-1">Strongly Agree</label>
		        <input type="radio" name="QA8" id="qa8-1" value="1" required>
			    <label for="qa8-2">Agree</label>
			    <input type="radio" name="QA8" id="qa8-2" value="2">
			    <label for="qa8-3">Neutral</label>
			    <input type="radio" name="QA8" id="qa8-3" value="3">
			    <label for="qa8-4">Disagree</label>
			    <input type="radio" name="QA8" id="qa8-4" value="4">
			    <label for="qa8-5">Strongly Disagree</label>
			    <input type="radio" name="QA8" id="qa8-5" value="5">
			</fieldset>
		  </li>
		  <li>
		    Comments (Within 500 words)
		    <textarea name="Comments_2" id="comments" placeholder="Share your thoughts here! "></textarea>
		  </li>
		</ol>
		  
		<div>
		  <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
		</div>
    </form> 
</div>
</body>
</html>